description: Recently sold: $245,000. Solid built cherished 1956 Rambler home in the heart of Roseville. 3 beds, 1 bath, oversized garage. Central commute with highway and interstate access to both downtowns of Minneapolis and S. Paul quickly within minutes. Near shopping, parks, trails, restaurants, and all that Roseville has to offer, including the high demand Roseville School District. 3 main level bedrooms and 1 walk-in shower creates all living facilities on one level - -3rd bedroom turned into main floor laundry for convenience--can easily be changed back to a bedroom. So many possibilities to add equity to create a 4th bedroom by installing an egress window in the basement. Rough-in already exists for a 2nd bathroom as well. Hardwood floors under the carpet. Spacious outdoor deck and private backyard presents plenty of opportunities to play, entertain and garden. Make this your next home before it is too late.

Recently sold: $104,000. Great opportunity, original owner waiting for your updates! Wonderful location with easy freeway access and near shopping and restaurants! Spacious 2 bedroom with natural sunlight throughout and tons of extra storage space. 2 balconies over looking the private court yard area. Enjoy all the amenities; pool, library, exercise room, sauna and tennis courts. Rentals permitted. Pets not allowed, companion pets only.

Recently sold: $140,000. Welcome home to your spacious turn-key ready condo with a large 78 sqft balcony overlooking a meticulously groomed lawn. Easy elevator ride down to your heated garage stall. After a long day you can relax in the Indoor Pool or warm up in the Hot Dry Sauna. Take advantage of the Tennis Courts and Fitness Center. Storage locker and laundry room just steps away. Easy access to HWY 36 & I35W and centrally located between St Paul & Mpls. One mile from Rosedale Mall and more than 36 restaurants nearby
